<ul><li>Solid sources should be transferred&nbsp;<b>using handling tools</b>&nbsp;such as tongs, or&nbsp;<b>using robots</b>.</li><li>To ensure the material is&nbsp;<b>as far from the user as practicible</b>, so the <b>intensity</b> of the&nbsp;\(\gamma\)&nbsp;radiation is as low as possible, and the user is <b>beyond the range</b> of a&nbsp;\(\alpha\)&nbsp;or&nbsp;\(\beta\)&nbsp;radiation from the source.</li></ul>